<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>MacMenuBar.com (中文)</title><link>https://macmenubar.com</link><description>精心整理的1300多款Mac菜单栏应用目录</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 08:10:25 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>叶子</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/leaf/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/leaf.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="Leaf" height="499" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/leaf.webp" width="500"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leaf 静默监控着在后台浪费内存的非活跃应用，并在适合退出时提醒你。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://satwiktungala.com/apps" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/C2VFDiDCjCk?si=r2juLhS8aaDeno2t" rel="noopener"&gt;观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 08:10:25 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>巧克力棒</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/chocolatebar/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/ChocolateBar.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="ChocolateBar" height="147" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/ChocolateBar.webp" width="1717"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ChocolateBar 在 Mac 菜单栏下方添加了第二行，让隐藏的被刘海遮挡的图标和打开的窗口重新显示出来。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://chocolatebar.app/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 11:36:39 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>复古Mac</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/retromac/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/retromac.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="RetroMac" height="472" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/retromac.webp" width="450"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RetroMac 能将你的 Mac 变成一个充满数字怀旧情怀的发光体，带有 CRT 闪烁、VHS 模糊效果以及来自 Mac OS 9 和 Windows XP 时代的经典桌面主题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://myretromac.app/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 08:56:12 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>智能关闭</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/smartclose/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/smartclose.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="SmartClose" height="245" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/smartclose.webp" width="300"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SmartClose 让 macOS 的行为更像 Windows：当应用程序的最后一个窗口关闭时，它会自动退出该应用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/mahirozdin/SmartClose" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 08:05:21 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>拖船</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/tug/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/tug.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="Tug" height="214" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/tug.webp" width="350"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tug 让设置计时器变得出奇的自然。从菜单栏向下拉动，当感觉时长合适时松开，计时器就会立即启动。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/tug-menu-bar-timer/id6768515427" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 06:05:33 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>